  "subject": "AAI information model extended with object to hold basic information about k8s resources.",
  "commit_message": "AAI information model extended with object to hold basic information\nabout k8s resources.\n\nAAI was extended with the object to hold basic information on kubernetes\nresources (CNF) and its relations to other entities like tenant, vnf\nmodules etc. More can be found here:\nhttps://wiki.onap.org/display/DW/Simplified+K8S+Resource+Model+-+IM\n\nIssue-ID: AAI-3205\nSigned-off-by: Marcin Krasowski <m.krasowski@samsung.com>\nChange-Id: Iec879011d604438c4ae0e2991bf945edd6f48e08\n",
